    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Kokoh Inti Arebama Tbk, together with its subsidiary, PT Karya Makmur Kreasi Prima, trades building materials in Indonesia. The company offers granite tiles, sanitary ware and fittings, vinyl tiles, adhesive tiles, mosaic tiles, vinyl flooring, ceramic/granite adhesives, and bathroom and kitchen cabinets. It also offers SCG and Bezt cement, SCG lightweight bricks, readymix concrete, SCG pipe and precast, SCG mortar, and Jayamix. The company offers its products under the KIA, Prime, Cotto, Fiona, Navera, Florence, Jayamix, and SCG Instant Beton brand names. It distributes its products through distributors; stores, such as Belanja Keramik; and portal web. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia. PT Kokoh Inti Arebama Tbk is a subsidiary of SCG Distribution Co., Ltd.",
